WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 21]

01:49.040 --> 01:50.290
The rain is bound to fall.

01:50.950 --> 01:52.330
I'm bound to be wed.

01:53.150 --> 01:54.380
Trees are ready to bloom.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.410
I'm ready to be married.

01:57.280 --> 01:59.130
Flowers long to bear fruit.

01:59.220 --> 02:00.480
[Tales of a Mortal Dream]

02:00.480 --> 02:01.540
I long to be married.

02:01.540 --> 02:03.900
[Su Jian]

02:05.430 --> 02:06.100
Is this

02:06.840 --> 02:08.100
the Little Pomegranate from the painting?

02:11.000 --> 02:12.180
So we are in...

02:14.400 --> 02:15.300
I was just thinking.

02:16.560 --> 02:17.470
This painting must carry

02:17.470 --> 02:18.900
the artist's memories and emotions.

02:20.190 --> 02:20.810
Maybe

02:21.400 --> 02:23.090
I could try the spell Master left me,

02:23.470 --> 02:25.060
like entering the Star Stone illusion.

02:25.630 --> 02:26.690
I didn't expect it to actually work.

02:27.520 --> 02:29.690
Cui Jun is good-looking.

02:30.520 --> 02:32.900
We've known each other since childhood and have been betrothed before birth.

02:33.400 --> 02:34.180
Cui Jun...

02:34.680 --> 02:35.460
The painter is

02:35.900 --> 02:36.770
Cui...

02:37.520 --> 02:38.440
Cui Jun?

02:38.800 --> 02:39.720
The one who painted this.

02:39.720 --> 02:40.990
But I've always treated him

02:41.240 --> 02:43.060
like a younger brother.

02:43.060 --> 02:44.350
How can anyone

02:44.350 --> 02:46.180
marry their own brother?

02:46.190 --> 02:47.530
Does that make any sense?

02:47.530 --> 02:49.210
Is that even reasonable?

02:50.000 --> 02:51.900
A forced melon is never sweet.

02:52.750 --> 02:53.420
Better let it rot

02:55.430 --> 02:56.620
on the vine.

02:59.910 --> 03:00.930
When

03:01.150 --> 03:02.140
will I ever

03:02.470 --> 03:04.210
have a love

03:04.630 --> 03:05.210
like in the stories?

03:06.400 --> 03:07.740
He chases, I run.

03:07.960 --> 03:09.490
I tease, he laughs.

03:09.840 --> 03:11.580
I faint, and he kisses me.

03:12.120 --> 03:13.620
How beautiful that must be.

03:16.710 --> 03:18.460
Oh, tree.

03:22.960 --> 03:23.810
Will there

03:24.280 --> 03:26.460
be an attractive, interesting man

03:26.750 --> 03:28.060
who falls in love with me?

03:28.470 --> 03:29.770
If the answer is yes,

03:29.770 --> 03:31.490
stay silent

03:32.030 --> 03:33.340
and don't move, alright?

03:52.080 --> 03:53.020
Handsome,

03:54.560 --> 03:55.530
who are you?

03:56.590 --> 03:58.340
You could get arrested

03:59.360 --> 04:00.930
for breaking into someone's home.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.060
I'm kind.

04:05.630 --> 04:06.370
I won't make a fuss over this.

04:06.910 --> 04:07.970
You should leave now.

04:08.430 --> 04:09.420
If fate allows,

04:09.840 --> 04:11.460
we may meet again someday.

04:12.750 --> 04:13.930
Go on.

04:14.430 --> 04:15.970
Hurry and leave.

04:17.120 --> 04:18.800
Don't get too mesmerized by my beauty,

04:18.800 --> 04:19.650
alright?

04:23.070 --> 04:23.810
Not leaving?

04:27.240 --> 04:28.780
So you want to stay and have a chat?

04:46.040 --> 04:46.890
Sir,

04:47.720 --> 04:49.100
sneaking up

04:49.240 --> 04:50.330
behind a lady

04:50.330 --> 04:51.980
and eavesdropping on her

04:52.240 --> 04:53.420
is a no-no.

04:53.430 --> 04:54.300
A little naughty.

04:56.160 --> 04:57.060
Tell me.

04:57.560 --> 04:58.370
From which line

04:58.430 --> 05:00.010
did you start listening?

05:00.430 --> 05:01.130
Was it

05:01.560 --> 05:02.570
"He chases, I run",

05:02.870 --> 05:05.540
or "I faint, and he kisses me"?

05:12.630 --> 05:14.060
The way you greet people

05:14.060 --> 05:14.930
is rather unique.

05:15.270 --> 05:17.930
You've definitely caught my attention.

05:19.720 --> 05:20.690
I'm Su Jian.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.100
What's your name?

05:22.390 --> 05:23.620
Where do you live?

05:23.950 --> 05:24.890
How old are you?

05:25.160 --> 05:25.930
Are you married?

05:26.190 --> 05:27.740
Have you picked names for our children yet?

05:28.830 --> 05:29.490
You're tired?

05:30.950 --> 05:32.330
The sky is still bright.

05:33.630 --> 05:34.540
No rush.

05:35.160 --> 05:36.100
How do I undo this?

05:36.830 --> 05:37.370
How...

05:37.680 --> 05:38.060
Help me.

05:39.160 --> 05:40.130
Sir.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.690
Why won't you speak?

05:43.630 --> 05:45.250
I often come to this weaving house,

05:45.800 --> 05:47.220
but I've never seen you before.

05:52.560 --> 05:53.620
Where are you going?

05:54.040 --> 05:55.420
It's raining outside.

05:55.680 --> 05:57.100
For a handsome man like you,

05:57.120 --> 05:58.370
if your clothes get soaked,

05:58.430 --> 05:59.690
you should take them off immediately

06:02.510 --> 06:03.220
and dry them,

06:04.390 --> 06:05.450
or you'll fall ill.

06:10.310 --> 06:10.860
So it's true.

06:12.310 --> 06:13.490
Han Ba can't speak.

06:15.720 --> 06:16.450
Wangyan.

06:18.720 --> 06:19.370
Wangyan.

06:20.310 --> 06:20.930
Jian.

06:26.120 --> 06:27.980
Si Feng once told me

06:29.160 --> 06:30.810
I had carried out a mission alone

06:30.950 --> 06:32.250
involving Han Ba.

06:33.390 --> 06:34.420
Could this be that mission?

06:35.630 --> 06:36.250
Mission?

06:38.190 --> 06:39.780
Disguising yourself as Su Jian's sister?

06:43.430 --> 06:44.980
Looks like you've cast the Word Magic

06:45.360 --> 06:46.780
over the entire Su family.

06:47.390 --> 06:49.100
Su Jian really believes you're her sister.

06:50.750 --> 06:52.420
Wangyan, you made iced treats again?

06:53.000 --> 06:53.800
How can you make ice treats

06:53.800 --> 06:55.130
in any season?

06:55.680 --> 06:57.300
Do you know magic?

06:58.160 --> 06:59.740
You must be the fairy

06:59.950 --> 07:01.420
from the stories.

07:02.360 --> 07:02.980
Is it good?

07:03.720 --> 07:04.980
I remember you once said

07:05.560 --> 07:07.250
you liked making iced treats for Lu Wuyi.

07:08.160 --> 07:08.740
It seems

07:09.510 --> 07:11.180
you've brought your real habits

07:11.750 --> 07:12.690
into the mission.

07:13.510 --> 07:14.660
Aren't you afraid of exposing yourself?

07:15.720 --> 07:17.490
You must've known

07:17.950 --> 07:19.330
I was troubled,

07:19.950 --> 07:21.420
so you made these iced treats

07:21.630 --> 07:23.250
to comfort me.

07:24.600 --> 07:25.690
What are you talking about?

07:26.360 --> 07:27.660
Lotus seeds.

07:28.480 --> 07:29.980
I'm as pitiful as these lotus seeds.

07:30.560 --> 07:31.450
My heart

07:31.950 --> 07:34.300
is like these iced lotus seeds.

07:34.600 --> 07:37.220
Col' an' bitter...

07:37.630 --> 07:38.860
Are you speaking in tongues?

07:39.310 --> 07:40.490
Cold

07:40.950 --> 07:42.810
and bitter.

07:44.480 --> 07:46.100
I know what you mean.

07:46.630 --> 07:47.740
It's been a whole month,

07:48.510 --> 07:50.250
and you're still not over

07:50.270 --> 07:51.130
that mute man?

07:51.240 --> 07:54.100
What? Mute?

07:54.510 --> 07:55.820
Wangyan, you're so ugly,

07:55.820 --> 07:56.420
but why do you speak so...

07:57.750 --> 07:59.310
I mean, you're so pretty,

07:59.310 --> 08:01.060
but why do you speak harshly?

08:01.630 --> 08:04.060
He's just steady and quiet.

08:05.000 --> 08:06.220
He complements me.

08:06.830 --> 08:07.890
Is he good-looking?

08:08.390 --> 08:09.100
Of course.

08:09.720 --> 08:10.890
Indeed, you complement each other.

08:12.830 --> 08:13.930
That's an insult.

08:14.190 --> 08:15.860
You really deserve a scolding.

08:16.270 --> 08:17.220
Do you remember

08:17.360 --> 08:18.430
you're supposed to marry Jun

08:18.430 --> 08:19.740
in three months?

08:20.040 --> 08:20.660
Jun?

08:21.190 --> 08:22.250
Who is that?

08:22.360 --> 08:23.570
Chenjun?

08:24.120 --> 08:25.250
Cui Jun.

08:27.560 --> 08:29.810
I don't want to marry him anymore.

08:34.070 --> 08:36.380
Cold and bitter.

08:38.600 --> 08:40.260
You're here brooding over it,

08:40.750 --> 08:42.020
while he can't even

08:42.550 --> 08:43.660
be bothered with you.

08:47.790 --> 08:49.020
They say in stories

08:49.550 --> 08:51.210
that when a woman pursues a man, it's like a thin veil between them.

08:51.750 --> 08:53.360
I've even gone as far

08:53.360 --> 08:54.380
as the barn next door.

08:55.000 --> 08:55.900
I refuse to believe

08:56.600 --> 08:57.970
I can't tear through this thin veil.

08:59.120 --> 08:59.810
Wangyan,

09:00.630 --> 09:01.810
just watch me.

09:08.670 --> 09:09.300
Wangyan.

09:10.600 --> 09:11.300
I choked myself.

09:15.200 --> 09:16.140
If

09:16.480 --> 09:17.970
you still won't speak,

09:18.120 --> 09:19.310
I'll show you

09:19.310 --> 09:20.380
what a fierce woman

09:20.840 --> 09:22.170
is like.

09:26.630 --> 09:27.090
Fine.

09:27.390 --> 09:29.060
I'll smash my head right here and die.

09:29.440 --> 09:30.260
Let's see

09:30.440 --> 09:32.380
if you'll call a physician for me then.

09:58.670 --> 09:59.450
This is a gift for you.

10:00.000 --> 10:01.060
You've barely passed twenty,

10:01.320 --> 10:03.210
it's the perfect age to carry an old man's fan.

10:04.270 --> 10:06.180
Honestly, I was worried you're too handsome,

10:06.670 --> 10:08.090
and other girls might start eyeing you.

10:09.030 --> 10:10.140
This old man's fan

10:10.480 --> 10:11.730
will do just the trick.

10:11.750 --> 10:13.810
It'll make your lofty, noble charm

10:14.080 --> 10:15.690
a little questionable

10:16.200 --> 10:18.500
and make you less appealing to other women.

10:22.240 --> 10:23.420
I've given you a gift.

10:23.790 --> 10:25.090
Won't you at least say thank you?

10:35.790 --> 10:36.730
My name is Su Jian.

10:37.200 --> 10:38.420
What's yours?

10:44.480 --> 10:45.210
You won't even tell me

10:45.240 --> 10:46.810
your name?

10:47.480 --> 10:48.690
If I don't know

10:48.690 --> 10:49.810
your name,

10:50.320 --> 10:51.330
how am I supposed

10:51.330 --> 10:52.060
to match our birth charts

10:52.080 --> 10:53.610
and figure out

10:53.610 --> 10:54.420
when we'll get married?

11:08.750 --> 11:09.730
Do I

11:10.080 --> 11:11.180
look pretty today?

11:12.150 --> 11:13.420
What a delicate flower.

11:13.750 --> 11:15.020
If you don't pick it now,

11:16.000 --> 11:16.810
it might belong

11:19.750 --> 11:21.500
to another man tomorrow.

11:22.000 --> 11:22.420
I...

11:28.380 --> 11:35.220
♪Who granted me this endless pain to wake me from my dream?♪

11:35.540 --> 11:41.980
♪All I want is to close my eyes, wave it all away, and sink into this illusion♪

11:42.700 --> 11:45.860
♪A fleeting soul that caught my eye in this mortal world♪

11:46.180 --> 11:50.060
♪How many hearts still burn so bright?♪

11:50.860 --> 11:55.620
♪I remain guarding this city of bitterness♪

11:56.060 --> 12:02.420
♪Who in this world wrote these cruel, heartless rules?♪

12:02.740 --> 12:09.380
♪That those who wait to reunite are left only with regret?♪

12:10.060 --> 12:13.300
♪Time wears the heart away♪

12:13.460 --> 12:17.580
♪What becomes of longing when the heart is gone?♪

12:18.300 --> 12:22.780
♪A devoted soul chasing the setting sun♪

12:22.790 --> 12:24.540
You always manage to find me.

12:27.390 --> 12:29.140
You always hide in the dark.

12:29.670 --> 12:31.180
Of course no one else can see you.

12:33.240 --> 12:34.450
But I can.

12:34.870 --> 12:36.020
But I can.

12:36.600 --> 12:37.450
My heart.

12:38.320 --> 12:39.060
My heart.

12:39.910 --> 12:41.610
Can feel you are here.

12:55.030 --> 12:56.300
I remember everything now.

13:01.720 --> 13:03.060
But in my memory,

13:04.630 --> 13:06.660
I was saying that to someone else.

13:07.200 --> 13:07.810
Wangyan,

13:09.200 --> 13:09.930
thank you.

13:10.320 --> 13:11.730
You're the only one who can see me.

13:12.910 --> 13:14.810
You always hide in the dark.

13:15.510 --> 13:17.450
Of course no one else can see you,

13:19.440 --> 13:20.420
but I can.

13:21.600 --> 13:22.330
My heart

13:23.960 --> 13:25.660
can feel you're here.

13:31.400 --> 13:32.370
Is it Lu Wuyi?

13:40.720 --> 13:42.090
There's no moon tonight.

13:45.540 --> 13:46.930
The moon is always there.

13:47.910 --> 13:50.020
It's just being mischievous tonight.

13:50.470 --> 13:51.570
It's hiding.

13:52.600 --> 13:54.540
The moon is meant to shine,

13:55.120 --> 13:56.780
to be admired, to be written into poems,

13:57.750 --> 13:59.300
to carry people's longing and praise.

14:00.030 --> 14:01.180
But tonight,

14:01.180 --> 14:02.850
no one can see it.

14:04.440 --> 14:05.450
Will it feel sad?

14:07.790 --> 14:08.610
Jian,

14:10.390 --> 14:11.730
are you talking about yourself?

14:18.750 --> 14:20.090
I am sad.

14:21.630 --> 14:22.330
Wangyan,

14:23.440 --> 14:24.300
you were right.

14:24.630 --> 14:26.500
It's always just been me.

14:27.080 --> 14:28.850
He's never responded to me.

14:29.960 --> 14:32.060
He wouldn't even tell me his name.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.090
He doesn't love you.

14:36.990 --> 14:38.450
But Cui Jun does.

14:38.870 --> 14:39.900
And I love you too.

14:41.670 --> 14:42.930
To me,

14:43.480 --> 14:45.140
you're the most important person.

14:46.440 --> 14:48.330
I'll stay with you forever.

14:49.790 --> 14:50.450
Jian,

14:51.790 --> 14:52.780
sleep.

14:53.670 --> 14:54.660
Have a good dream.

14:55.390 --> 14:57.180
When the dream ends,

14:58.030 --> 14:59.780
I'll wake you.

15:02.480 --> 15:03.690
And if I don't,

15:05.480 --> 15:07.260
don't ever wake up.

15:16.150 --> 15:18.420
Han Ba still refuses to speak.

15:19.630 --> 15:20.210
Jian,

15:21.790 --> 15:22.900
I'm sorry to put you through this.

15:36.720 --> 15:37.300
Wait.

15:43.150 --> 15:44.200
Are you the quiet man

15:44.200 --> 15:45.540
my sister likes?

15:50.750 --> 15:52.060
She suddenly fell ill

15:52.270 --> 15:53.210
and has been unconscious.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.810
The physician said it's a matter of the heart.

15:55.320 --> 15:57.450
Only the voice of the one she loves can bring her back.

16:10.510 --> 16:12.260
I don't have a human name.

16:13.630 --> 16:14.780
I only have a demon name.

16:17.630 --> 16:18.420
I'm Han Ba.

16:19.630 --> 16:20.420
And

16:21.270 --> 16:23.330
the moment I speak,

16:24.000 --> 16:26.380
drought will fall upon the world.

16:28.720 --> 16:30.780
I've lived inside a tree

16:31.960 --> 16:33.180
day after day,

16:34.200 --> 16:35.180
I was so bored.

16:36.670 --> 16:38.380
No one ever spoke to me

16:40.030 --> 16:41.210
until I met you.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.450
Oh, tree.

16:43.600 --> 16:44.540
Will there

16:44.540 --> 16:46.570
be an attractive, interesting man

16:46.600 --> 16:47.810
who falls in love with me?

16:47.810 --> 16:49.450
If the answer is yes,

16:49.750 --> 16:51.610
stay silent

16:53.630 --> 16:54.780
and don't move, alright?

17:06.240 --> 17:07.210
Meeting you

17:08.680 --> 17:11.330
was like a flame melting ice.

17:12.310 --> 17:14.460
This world that was once indifferent to me

17:18.590 --> 17:20.850
suddenly came alive.

17:25.350 --> 17:26.650
Even if I couldn't speak,

17:27.110 --> 17:28.700
just watching you talk

17:30.070 --> 17:31.020
made me happy.

17:35.590 --> 17:37.220
I wanted to answer you.

17:38.310 --> 17:40.410
I wanted to tell you

17:40.920 --> 17:42.060
everything I felt.

17:43.510 --> 17:44.260
But

17:45.440 --> 17:47.300
if I ever responded to your love,

17:48.480 --> 17:50.020
everyone you cherish in this world

17:51.240 --> 17:52.370
would be destroyed by me.

17:58.350 --> 18:00.130
You like stories, don't you?

18:02.030 --> 18:03.090
Stop sleeping.

18:04.310 --> 18:05.410
I'll tell you a story.

18:07.350 --> 18:08.220
Wake up,

18:10.310 --> 18:11.020
alright?

18:26.640 --> 18:27.500
It works.

18:32.240 --> 18:32.980
Jian,

18:33.640 --> 18:35.500
did you hear the voice of the man you love?

18:37.750 --> 18:38.940
The dream is over.

18:40.270 --> 18:41.700
Wake up now.

18:51.550 --> 18:52.300
As expected.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.260
Only the one she loves

18:54.440 --> 18:55.500
could wake her.

18:59.750 --> 19:00.740
This is bad!

19:00.880 --> 19:01.980
- This is bad! - Quiet.

19:01.980 --> 19:02.650
Something's happened!

19:03.240 --> 19:03.890
Su Jian,

19:03.960 --> 19:05.060
why are you still here?

19:05.240 --> 19:06.170
You should go take a look.

19:06.400 --> 19:07.810
Your mother fought someone over water

19:07.830 --> 19:09.130
and was beaten to death.

19:19.680 --> 19:20.810
What was my mission

19:23.200 --> 19:24.130
back then?

19:25.590 --> 19:27.020
Wu Wangyan's mission

19:27.510 --> 19:28.610
was to capture the water demons

19:28.610 --> 19:30.130
hiding in the underground waterways

19:30.480 --> 19:31.740
of Luo'an.

19:32.480 --> 19:33.570
But what does that have to do

19:33.750 --> 19:35.500
with making you speak?

19:36.000 --> 19:36.980
Aren't you supposed to be smart?

19:39.030 --> 19:40.020
Can't you figure that out?

19:40.270 --> 19:41.260
Of course I can.

19:41.350 --> 19:42.700
I just want to hear you say it.

19:44.200 --> 19:45.780
If she wanted to flush out the water demons,

19:47.270 --> 19:49.810
she had to make Han Ba speak, which would trigger a drought,

19:50.680 --> 19:51.940
dry up water sources,

19:52.550 --> 19:53.410
and force the water demons

19:53.680 --> 19:55.980
out of the tangled underground waterways.

19:56.680 --> 19:58.130
There's no way

19:59.110 --> 19:59.960
I would've agreed

19:59.960 --> 20:01.170
to cause such devastation.

20:02.160 --> 20:02.940
That's why

20:03.000 --> 20:04.890
Jiu Ying erased my memory.

20:08.510 --> 20:10.610
Drought brings conflict and unrest.

20:11.830 --> 20:13.780
As fear and hatred multiply,

20:14.070 --> 20:15.460
Jiu Ying feeds on them

20:16.110 --> 20:17.500
and becomes stronger.

20:19.310 --> 20:20.220
I didn't understand back then.

20:22.400 --> 20:23.810
Now I do.

20:25.160 --> 20:27.330
That was Jiu Ying's true intention.

20:34.480 --> 20:35.260
If I didn't speak,

20:36.200 --> 20:37.220
I couldn't save her.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.330
But if I did,

20:41.030 --> 20:42.220
I harmed her

20:43.350 --> 20:44.810
and the entire mortal world.

20:48.350 --> 20:49.540
I don't have a mother anymore.

21:00.030 --> 21:01.650
I know my sins run deep,

21:02.200 --> 21:03.740
but I never dared tell her the truth.

21:05.240 --> 21:05.810
Not until

21:06.590 --> 21:08.500
the double-flower hunter came to bring me to justice.

21:17.350 --> 21:17.980
Han Ba,

21:18.790 --> 21:20.060
you've acted recklessly

21:20.400 --> 21:21.500
and brought drought upon the land,

21:22.270 --> 21:23.810
turning Luo'an into scorched earth,

21:24.400 --> 21:25.540
leaving countless lives in ruin.

21:26.310 --> 21:27.940
By the order of Master Chi Wen,

21:28.200 --> 21:30.060
we're here to take you back to the Shilin Sect to face judgment.

21:30.110 --> 21:31.060
You'd better not try something silly.

21:31.400 --> 21:32.130
My martial senior

21:32.510 --> 21:33.260
is very powerful.

21:35.680 --> 21:36.460
He's getting away.

21:38.310 --> 21:39.570
- I shouldn't have changed my mind... - Si Feng!

21:39.570 --> 21:40.700
...and brought a reckless fool like you along.

21:41.110 --> 21:41.810
Wait outside.

21:41.960 --> 21:42.500
Si Feng!

21:43.350 --> 21:43.980
Si Feng!

21:44.310 --> 21:44.940
Si Feng!

21:45.400 --> 21:46.260
Wait for me.

21:47.000 --> 21:47.920
I'll soon become

21:47.920 --> 21:49.090
a powerful double-flower hunter.

21:50.140 --> 21:50.840
Si Feng,

21:51.270 --> 21:52.090
I finally found you.

21:52.240 --> 21:52.780
Careful!

21:53.240 --> 21:54.020
Careful of what?

21:56.440 --> 21:57.370
I don't want to hurt you.

21:57.440 --> 21:57.850
Stand aside.

21:58.830 --> 21:59.610
I wanted to.

22:00.070 --> 22:00.460
You!

22:05.590 --> 22:06.170
Si Feng,

22:06.270 --> 22:07.060
he's got backup.

22:07.880 --> 22:08.740
Anyway, two against two.

22:09.160 --> 22:09.810
It's even.

22:11.790 --> 22:12.780
Can you even beat her?

22:13.400 --> 22:14.790
She's a thousand-year-old nine-tailed fox

22:14.790 --> 22:16.300
from the Formless Moon Sect.

22:17.070 --> 22:18.060
She's a fox demon?

22:18.680 --> 22:20.070
The double-flower hunter from the Shilin Sect

22:20.070 --> 22:21.460
is quite heartless.

22:22.310 --> 22:23.810
How can you bring yourself

22:24.400 --> 22:26.090
to tear apart a couple in love?

22:27.350 --> 22:28.130
How amusing.

22:28.880 --> 22:30.370
A fox demon from the Formless Moon Sect

22:31.070 --> 22:32.650
lecturing me on human sentiment?

22:33.880 --> 22:35.090
What are you doing here?

22:35.790 --> 22:36.940
I'm here to rid the world

22:37.310 --> 22:38.460
of water demons.

22:39.110 --> 22:41.330
Whether your sect creates evil or destroys it,

22:42.030 --> 22:43.170
can you really tell the difference?

22:44.790 --> 22:45.740
No matter what,

22:46.640 --> 22:48.410
I won't let you take Han Ba away.

22:49.480 --> 22:50.460
The fault isn't his.

22:51.160 --> 22:52.090
He's innocent.

22:52.920 --> 22:53.940
Of course it isn't his fault.

22:54.070 --> 22:54.810
It's yours.

22:55.070 --> 22:56.460
You're the one who made him speak.

22:56.640 --> 22:57.890
You wretched fox.

22:57.960 --> 22:58.980
Don't think you can hide what you did.

22:59.440 --> 23:01.650
I've never sparred with a fox from the Formless Moon Sect.

23:02.110 --> 23:02.850
Today

23:03.400 --> 23:04.460
is the perfect chance.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.300
I've never fought alongside you, Si Feng.

23:06.310 --> 23:08.410
Time to show what I can do.

23:09.240 --> 23:09.780
Wait.

23:12.510 --> 23:14.170
The drought was indeed caused by me.

23:15.440 --> 23:17.650
I'll return to the Shilin Sect with you.

23:19.240 --> 23:19.810
But

23:20.830 --> 23:22.540
let me see her one last time

23:24.720 --> 23:25.890
and bid farewell to her.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.060
Please.

23:38.000 --> 23:38.700
So

23:39.270 --> 23:40.130
you are a demon.

23:42.200 --> 23:44.060
Why did you cause the drought?

23:47.240 --> 23:51.410
The drought killed my mother.

24:12.590 --> 24:13.890
I'll explain everything to Su Jian.

24:15.350 --> 24:16.330
It's not what she thinks.

24:18.550 --> 24:19.540
- It was me. - No need.

24:20.590 --> 24:22.130
I've hurt her enough.

24:24.810 --> 24:26.040
I can't let her know

24:28.350 --> 24:30.370
that the sister she loves was using her all along.

24:31.790 --> 24:32.890
Does the Formless Moon Sect

24:32.960 --> 24:34.480
have Word Magic

24:34.480 --> 24:35.940
that can alter memories?

24:38.270 --> 24:39.850
Can you make her forget me?

24:42.510 --> 24:43.500
Fairy,

24:44.400 --> 24:46.370
aren't your spells powerful?

24:47.510 --> 24:48.810
Can you make me forget him?

24:52.000 --> 24:52.700
Please.

25:28.070 --> 25:28.650
What?

25:29.160 --> 25:30.460
Can't bring yourself to do it?

25:32.000 --> 25:33.300
It's just

25:33.920 --> 25:35.460
their love is rare,

25:36.110 --> 25:37.570
like a precious treasure.

25:38.400 --> 25:39.260
I can't bear to destroy it.

25:46.590 --> 25:47.570
If you can't,

25:48.000 --> 25:49.060
use this.

26:15.270 --> 26:16.610
You've got the softest heart

26:17.480 --> 26:18.650
of any fox I've met.

26:20.480 --> 26:22.170
You left a hope

26:22.920 --> 26:23.850
for Su Jian and Han Ba.

26:38.880 --> 26:40.300
After Su Jian forgot me,

26:40.920 --> 26:42.830
I was ready to return to the Shilin Sect to accept punishment

26:42.830 --> 26:43.700
and end the drought.

26:44.750 --> 26:45.650
But I never expected

26:46.590 --> 26:47.370
Su Jian

26:48.240 --> 26:49.090
to seek revenge on the man

26:49.090 --> 26:50.890
who killed her mother.

26:52.680 --> 26:54.020
She was gravely wounded

26:56.310 --> 26:57.220
and fading fast.

27:07.750 --> 27:09.220
Your spiritual veins will shatter,

27:10.200 --> 27:11.810
and the backlash will destroy you

27:12.680 --> 27:13.810
after pouring your demon power into her.

27:32.030 --> 27:33.220
I only want her

27:34.310 --> 27:35.890
to stay alive

27:37.920 --> 27:39.130
and be happy.

28:01.830 --> 28:03.460
I grew up with Jian.

28:04.830 --> 28:06.020
Marrying her

28:06.880 --> 28:08.540
has always been my greatest wish.

28:10.200 --> 28:11.500
I'll take care of her

28:13.030 --> 28:14.020
for life,

28:14.960 --> 28:15.810
never leave her,

28:16.880 --> 28:17.850
never fail her.

28:20.270 --> 28:21.090
Don't worry.

28:22.440 --> 28:24.090
So Su Jian's fiancé

28:24.310 --> 28:25.780
knew everything all along.

28:26.590 --> 28:28.220
Did Su Jian tell him?

28:30.680 --> 28:31.650
When you truly love someone,

28:33.160 --> 28:34.370
how can any secret stay hidden?

28:35.640 --> 28:36.980
Everything we saw

28:38.640 --> 28:40.220
was Jun's memory.

28:41.340 --> 28:46.780
[Fifty years later]

28:46.780 --> 28:52.460
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

28:52.820 --> 28:58.020
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

29:00.100 --> 29:03.220
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you...♪

29:04.790 --> 29:06.300
I already know who the person in black is.

29:09.110 --> 29:09.810
Iced treats.

29:10.640 --> 29:11.540
Opening up to each other.

29:12.830 --> 29:14.090
Promising to stay together forever.

29:15.680 --> 29:16.500
Those were your memories

29:16.500 --> 29:17.890
with Lu Wuyi.

29:18.960 --> 29:20.060
But now they're happening

29:20.060 --> 29:21.170
between you and Su Jian.

29:22.780 --> 29:24.500
Maybe the memories in that painting

29:26.680 --> 29:27.540
are fake.

29:27.590 --> 29:28.460
True or false,

29:29.070 --> 29:30.540
we'll find out once we ask Han Ba.

29:33.000 --> 29:34.330
But I'd rather believe

29:35.350 --> 29:37.090
your story with Lu Wuyi

29:37.640 --> 29:39.130
was fabricated by Jiu Ying.

29:40.200 --> 29:41.540
Not just the memories,

29:42.720 --> 29:43.940
even Lu Wuyi herself

29:45.160 --> 29:46.260
may have been made up.

29:49.270 --> 29:50.980
She stole the manuscript

29:53.000 --> 29:54.650
because she didn't want you to find out the truth.

29:56.310 --> 29:57.940
But Ji Ling said they were together.

29:59.920 --> 30:01.220
Ji Ling is defending her.

30:15.200 --> 30:15.740
Wu,

30:16.720 --> 30:17.610
I know it's you.

30:18.550 --> 30:19.890
The only one who could withstand

30:19.960 --> 30:21.370
Wu Shiguang and Han Ba's power

30:22.550 --> 30:23.330
is you.

30:24.680 --> 30:25.410
But

30:26.070 --> 30:27.980
they never attacked you before.

30:28.680 --> 30:30.890
When did you absorb their power?

30:31.110 --> 30:31.610
Wuyi.

30:33.110 --> 30:33.700
Wuyi.

30:35.720 --> 30:36.370
Ji,

30:37.440 --> 30:38.060
help me.

30:40.790 --> 30:41.610
I'm begging you.

30:48.030 --> 30:49.650
I didn't give you away to Wu Wangyan.

30:50.160 --> 30:51.410
So, will you tell me

30:52.310 --> 30:53.570
what's really going on?

30:56.830 --> 30:57.460
Wu.

31:06.030 --> 31:06.650
Wu.

31:08.440 --> 31:09.810
Tell me the truth.

31:32.200 --> 31:32.940
Backlash...

31:35.070 --> 31:36.060
Your Word Magic

31:36.720 --> 31:38.220
is stronger than Xiaowei's?

31:40.110 --> 31:40.700
Wu,

31:42.440 --> 31:44.170
what happened to you?

31:45.310 --> 31:46.160
Why did you

31:46.160 --> 31:47.700
use Word Magic on Mu Long?

31:57.000 --> 31:58.650
Why did you take those manuscript pages?

32:00.830 --> 32:01.570
If you won't speak,

32:03.200 --> 32:04.330
I'll ask Wu Wangyan.

32:05.830 --> 32:06.410
Don't!

32:18.790 --> 32:19.780
Those pages

32:24.310 --> 32:25.460
contain a secret

32:26.030 --> 32:27.850
I never wanted Wangyan to know.

32:30.750 --> 32:32.540
I would lose her.

32:35.880 --> 32:36.780
What secret?

32:42.110 --> 32:44.130
I'm not a fox from the Formless Moon Sect.

32:49.750 --> 32:50.740
I'm not even

32:54.490 --> 32:55.610
a demon.

32:58.000 --> 32:59.170
I'm a monster.

32:59.260 --> 33:02.020
♪How should this story be told...♪

33:02.680 --> 33:04.940
I'm a piece of trash

33:08.920 --> 33:09.700
stitched together by Jiu Ying.

33:12.590 --> 33:14.060
I learned that all my memories

33:14.960 --> 33:16.310
are fake

33:16.310 --> 33:17.260
from Mu Long's story.

33:20.720 --> 33:21.460
So

33:22.920 --> 33:24.370
I went to confront Jiu Ying.

33:25.960 --> 33:26.570
Jiu Ying,

33:27.190 --> 33:28.080
come out.

33:31.260 --> 33:33.900
♪How do you measure memory♪

33:34.180 --> 33:39.020
♪To cut the past into clothes to wear?♪

33:39.130 --> 33:40.160
Why

33:41.550 --> 33:43.330
do my memories with Wangyan

33:43.920 --> 33:45.740
appear in Mu Long's story?

33:47.720 --> 33:48.410
Why

33:49.720 --> 33:51.740
are Little Pomegranate and Wangyan's stories

33:52.720 --> 33:54.200
exactly the same

33:54.200 --> 33:54.980
as mine?

33:56.180 --> 33:57.180
♪Don't be afraid...♪

33:57.200 --> 33:57.980
Just why?

34:00.680 --> 34:02.060
What did you do

34:03.440 --> 34:05.090
to my memories?

34:08.180 --> 34:11.580
♪You brave the wind and bear the rain♪

34:12.100 --> 34:18.900
♪Thank you for the shelter of your shade♪

34:20.220 --> 34:23.740
♪Moon sets, crows cry♪

34:24.130 --> 34:27.620
♪Time slips by, a swift steed in flight...♪

34:27.800 --> 34:30.690
When the Formless Moon Sect attacked the flood dragons,

34:31.360 --> 34:32.980
they fell into the trap of Xie Lingxi

34:34.000 --> 34:35.290
and were completely wiped out.

34:38.110 --> 34:39.380
Before they were reborn,

34:40.280 --> 34:42.420
Jiu Ying took a part

34:43.390 --> 34:45.500
from each of their bodies,

34:46.510 --> 34:47.770
flesh, veins, spirit, or qi,

34:50.030 --> 34:50.900
and stitched them together

34:53.190 --> 34:54.460
to create me.

34:59.320 --> 35:01.650
And what she took from Wangyan

35:05.510 --> 35:06.380
was her heart.

35:08.110 --> 35:08.820
What about you?

35:13.510 --> 35:14.290
Where is your heart?

35:17.320 --> 35:18.210
That explains

35:20.070 --> 35:21.570
why Wu Wangyan dotes on you so much.

35:24.280 --> 35:25.060
That's because

35:26.800 --> 35:27.900
you are her heart.

35:31.920 --> 35:33.900
But Jiu Ying placed a spirit fragment

35:34.440 --> 35:36.060
in her heart.

35:45.110 --> 35:47.130
The last fragment you've been searching for

35:52.480 --> 35:53.460
is with me.

36:17.800 --> 36:18.940
I knew it all along.

36:23.550 --> 36:24.460
I just

36:26.360 --> 36:27.610
didn't understand

36:30.150 --> 36:32.170
why you stayed by my side,

36:34.230 --> 36:36.210
yet I couldn't sense that last fragment.

36:37.630 --> 36:38.290
Turns out

36:39.630 --> 36:41.570
it was hidden in Wangyan's heart.

36:42.960 --> 36:43.980
Her heart

36:46.480 --> 36:47.690
has always been protecting you.

36:49.400 --> 36:50.380
Wangyan's heart...

36:53.070 --> 36:54.090
When our hearts

36:54.760 --> 36:56.420
come into this world,

36:57.480 --> 36:58.570
one way or another,

36:59.320 --> 37:01.170
they are bound to be marked by love.

37:02.920 --> 37:03.540
Love

37:05.000 --> 37:07.610
is the oldest

37:09.550 --> 37:11.090
and the most powerful spell of all.

37:15.840 --> 37:17.210
Before any of us were revived,

37:17.210 --> 37:18.290
Jiu Ying

37:19.840 --> 37:21.500
altered our memories.

37:28.000 --> 37:28.650
Wangyan.

37:29.840 --> 37:31.610
Wangyan, you made iced treats again.

38:05.840 --> 38:06.540
Wangyan.

38:07.550 --> 38:08.130
Let's go.

38:15.230 --> 38:16.730
You always manage to find me.

38:17.190 --> 38:19.060
You always hide in the dark.

38:19.320 --> 38:20.310
Of course no one else

38:20.310 --> 38:21.290
can see you.

38:22.360 --> 38:23.380
But I can.

38:24.400 --> 38:25.130
My heart

38:25.960 --> 38:27.610
can feel you're here.

38:49.710 --> 38:51.380
Xie Lingxi killed all of you.

38:52.230 --> 38:53.290
But he didn't know

38:53.880 --> 38:55.020
the Power of the Moon

38:55.800 --> 38:57.090
is eternal.

39:08.550 --> 39:10.090
When everyone was reborn,

39:10.760 --> 39:12.690
they took those altered memories

39:13.190 --> 39:14.130
as truth.

39:15.960 --> 39:16.940
They believed

39:16.940 --> 39:17.980
they had a younger sister like me.

39:24.440 --> 39:25.650
I used to think

39:25.920 --> 39:27.020
I was the new moon,

39:28.230 --> 39:29.650
one of the moon phases.

39:31.630 --> 39:33.130
But in the end,

39:37.550 --> 39:38.730
I was never real.

39:42.590 --> 39:44.690
I'm nothing but a shameless thief.

39:47.360 --> 39:49.250
I stole their memories

39:51.110 --> 39:52.540
to piece together a life of my own.

39:56.920 --> 39:57.500
Full moon,

39:59.760 --> 40:00.340
waning gibbous,

40:01.440 --> 40:02.170
last-quarter,

40:04.070 --> 40:04.730
waxing gibbous,

40:05.760 --> 40:06.650
first-quarter,

40:07.840 --> 40:08.500
waning crescent,

40:09.880 --> 40:10.650
and waxing crescent.

40:12.320 --> 40:13.340
In the sky,

40:18.230 --> 40:19.980
there was never a place for me.

40:42.510 --> 40:43.610
Your place

40:45.630 --> 40:46.650
was never in the sky.

40:49.880 --> 40:50.860
It's in my heart.

40:53.780 --> 40:56.100
♪We count down to tomorrow...♪

40:57.630 --> 40:59.130
Nothing between us

41:00.710 --> 41:01.900
is fake.

41:03.590 --> 41:05.380
From the day we met,

41:07.880 --> 41:10.130
every moment this world has witnessed

41:13.230 --> 41:15.060
belongs only to us.

41:16.140 --> 41:18.660
♪Let's go back in time♪

41:19.020 --> 41:21.300
♪Snow piled high by the window♪

41:21.380 --> 41:24.660
♪Under sparks of fireworks, we♪

41:24.780 --> 41:26.980
♪Smiled through tears so sweet♪

41:27.100 --> 41:30.180
♪You said you'd find a little corner♪

41:30.220 --> 41:32.500
♪And give me ten thousand wildflowers♪

41:32.540 --> 41:38.420
♪Softly telling me you'd stay with me forever♪

41:38.660 --> 41:41.340
♪Under the world's small roof♪

41:42.100 --> 41:45.100
♪You're right here by my side...♪

41:49.230 --> 41:51.380
But how did Wuyi come to know all this?

41:53.960 --> 41:55.940
She arrived at the inn at the same time as us.

41:56.760 --> 41:58.210
How did you learn

41:59.710 --> 42:01.130
the truth?

42:04.880 --> 42:06.060
Maybe

42:07.920 --> 42:09.940
Lu Wuyi went through something we don't know about.

42:14.190 --> 42:14.860
Wu,

42:16.840 --> 42:17.540
tell me.

42:19.230 --> 42:20.380
No matter what happens,

42:22.000 --> 42:23.940
I'll face it with you.

42:27.920 --> 42:28.880
This isn't the first time

42:28.880 --> 42:30.340
I've been through this.

42:31.760 --> 42:32.980
The Yanbi Inn.

42:34.400 --> 42:35.540
This drought.

42:36.960 --> 42:38.130
It's not the first time,

42:39.510 --> 42:40.730
not the tenth,

42:42.360 --> 42:43.690
but countless times.

42:58.360 --> 42:59.980
From the moment we entered the inn,

43:00.000 --> 43:01.290
at the Zi hour that night,

43:02.070 --> 43:03.610
I've been trapped in a loop,

43:04.590 --> 43:05.940
reliving it over and over again.

43:09.540 --> 43:16.500
[First rewind]

43:57.000 --> 44:00.020
Big drumstick...

44:02.000 --> 44:02.650
Miss Mu.

44:04.880 --> 44:06.250
- Miss Mu. - What are you trying to do?

44:06.800 --> 44:07.170
You...

44:07.360 --> 44:09.130
You've stained my manuscript.

44:48.920 --> 44:50.770
I've relived everything again and again.

44:51.840 --> 44:53.340
I've endured countless attacks from Han Ba,

44:53.670 --> 44:54.500
Wu Shiguang,

44:54.960 --> 44:56.940
and Li Jie.

44:57.710 --> 44:58.960
That's why none of their spells

44:58.960 --> 44:59.900
can harm me.

45:00.960 --> 45:02.130
And my Word Magic

45:03.320 --> 45:04.460
has surpassed yours.

45:07.190 --> 45:08.460
Time reversal?

45:10.630 --> 45:12.570
How could Jiu Ying possess such power?

45:15.000 --> 45:15.940
I don't know.

45:22.630 --> 45:23.860
Time reversal

45:24.760 --> 45:26.540
damages the body,

45:27.230 --> 45:27.770
doesn't it?

45:29.510 --> 45:30.020
Yes.

45:32.320 --> 45:33.940
And the toll only gets worse each time.

45:38.760 --> 45:39.420
So

45:40.030 --> 45:40.820
Ji,

45:41.400 --> 45:42.170
help me.

45:44.400 --> 45:45.340
I'm afraid.

45:46.230 --> 45:48.090
I'm afraid that once Wangyan finds out the truth,

45:48.960 --> 45:49.900
she'll hate me.

45:51.030 --> 45:52.460
I don't want to lose her.

45:54.190 --> 45:54.820
Don't be afraid.

45:56.230 --> 45:57.860
You stole the manuscript

45:58.960 --> 46:00.650
and used Word Magic on Mu Long.

46:01.800 --> 46:03.420
Wangyan will never find out what happened.

46:07.070 --> 46:07.540
No.

46:08.760 --> 46:09.980
There's another way.

46:12.190 --> 46:13.770
All the truth and memories

46:14.000 --> 46:15.980
are stored inside Mu Long's horn pendant.

46:16.710 --> 46:18.250
Every time time reverses,

46:19.030 --> 46:20.280
I can't stop Wangyan

46:20.280 --> 46:21.730
from discovering what's inside.

46:23.110 --> 46:24.020
Maybe

46:26.000 --> 46:28.380
that's why I'm trapped here.

46:30.480 --> 46:32.570
My fear of losing her

46:34.800 --> 46:36.020
has bound me to this place.

46:39.280 --> 46:40.340
But this time,

46:42.400 --> 46:43.570
I know the truth.

46:45.190 --> 46:46.650
Maybe this is fate.

46:48.280 --> 46:50.090
It's giving me a chance to change everything for you.

46:54.280 --> 46:55.380
You're willing to help me?

46:59.710 --> 47:01.650
I would do anything for you.

47:05.960 --> 47:08.020
Take that pendant back for me.

47:09.590 --> 47:10.500
Help me.

47:54.500 --> 47:59.900
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams♪

48:00.580 --> 48:06.580
♪I stay silent, afraid the fire in my heart will rise♪

48:07.460 --> 48:10.100
♪Reed flowers sway with burning heat♪

48:10.780 --> 48:13.580
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

48:14.220 --> 48:19.460
♪I am only a murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

48:21.180 --> 48:26.900
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

48:27.460 --> 48:33.500
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

48:34.180 --> 48:37.460
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

48:38.100 --> 48:41.060
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness♪

48:41.620 --> 48:46.700
♪Watching the corner of your lips stained with a touch of dark crimson♪

48:48.300 --> 48:54.060
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

48:54.660 --> 49:00.100
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

49:01.980 --> 49:04.940
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

49:05.460 --> 49:08.420
♪In winter, I'll boil snow to warm the fading dusk♪

49:08.940 --> 49:14.140
♪Of joy and sorrow, of countless softly lit homes, I'll speak to you♪

49:14.660 --> 49:20.700
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from♪

49:21.300 --> 49:27.540
♪Draining every joy and sorrow, crushing the void within the heart♪

49:28.020 --> 49:36.340
♪With white hair and dewy eyes, I sigh for youth, when words defied the heart♪

49:36.940 --> 49:43.740
♪Whose dream lies buried beneath the cenotaph?♪
